- content_for :page_title do
  .center
    %i.f7-icons.color-white book_fill
    .right Excellent Believer
.view.view-main
  .pages
    .page
      / page-content has additional login-screen content
      .page-content
        .content-block-title Welcome!
        .content-block
          %p Excellent Believer facilitates reading the Life-Studies in groups. We'd like to encourage everyone to read two Life-Studies of Genesis a week. However if your church has another reading schedule please follow that. If your group is reading the Life-Study of Genesis, don't forget to tag your group with "Genesis"
        .content-block
          = link_to 'Sign In', new_user_session_path, class: 'button button-big button-red button-fill'
